quran[8{c,v,t}:
40,26,aur firaon bola ke mujhe chhorro ke moose ko qatal kardoon aur woh apne perwar-digaar ko blale. mujhe dar hai ke woh ( kahin ) tumahray deen ko nah badal day ya malik mein fasaad ( nah ) peda kardey
40,27,moose ne kaha ke mein har mutaqabbir se jo hisaab ke din ( yani qayamat ) par imaan nahi lata. apne aur tumahray perwar-digaar ki panah le chuka hon
40,28,aur firaon ke logon mein se aik momin shakhs jo apne imaan ko posheeda rakhta tha kehnay lagakiya tum aisay shakhs ko qatal karna chahtay ho jo kehta hai ke mera perwar-digaar khuda hai aur woh tumahray perwar-digaar ( ki taraf ) se nishanain bhi le kar aaya hai. aur agar woh jhoota hoga to is ke jhoot ka zarrar isi ko hoga. aur agar sacha hoga to koi sa azaab jis ka woh tum se wada karta hai tum par waqay ho kar rahay ga. be shak khuda is shakhs ko hadaayat nahi deta jo be lehaaz jhoota hai
40,29,ae qoum aaj tumhari hi badshahat hai aur tum hi malik mein ghalib ho. ( lekin ) agar hum par khuda ka azaab agaya to ( is ke daur karne ke liye ) hamari madad kon kere ga. firaon ne kaha ke mein tumhe wohi baat smjhata hon jo mujhe sojhi hai aur wohi raah batata hon jis mein bhalai hai
40,30,to jo momin tha woh kehnay laga ke ae qoum mujhe tumhari nisbat khauf hai ke ( mbada ) tum par aur ummton ki terhan ke din ka azaab aajay
40,31,yani ) Nooh ki qoum aur Aad aur smod aur jo log un ke peechay hue hain un ke haal ki terhan ( tumhara haal nah hojaye ) aur khuda to bundon par zulm karna nahi chahta
40,32,aur ae qoum mujhe tumhari nisbat pukaar ke din ( yani qayamat ) ka khauf hai
40,33,jis din tum peeth phair kar ( qayamat ke din se ) bhago ge ( is din ) tum ko koi ( azaab ) khuda se bachanay wala nah hoga. aur jis shakhs ko khuda gumraah kere is ko koi hadaayat dainay wala nahi
